    - "This spec extends multiprocessing_extra87.zspec.zsdl."
    - "This spec covers: wave 250 theme — multiprocessing.Pool (pool.Pool class) __dict__ membership. NEW in extra88: pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('map')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('starmap')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('apply')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('apply_async')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('map_async')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('starmap_async')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('close')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('terminate')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('join')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('imap')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('imap_unordered')==True; pool.Pool.__dict__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('mappingproxy')==True. All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('map') == True. map() is defined directly on Pool in Lib/multiprocessing/pool.py. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('starmap') == True. starmap() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('apply') == True. apply() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('apply_async') == True. apply_async() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('map_async') == True. map_async() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('starmap_async') == True. starmap_async() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('close') == True. close() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('terminate') == True. terminate() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('join') == True. join() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('imap') == True. imap() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__contains__('imap_unordered') == True. imap_unordered() is defined directly on Pool. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__dict__.__class__.__name__ == 'mappingproxy'. The class __dict__ is a mappingproxy instance, which is the standard type for class __dict__ objects in CPython. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
  created_at: "2026-04-10T00:00:00Z"

